Sussan bụ onye na-ere ejiji ụmụ nwanyị n'Australia, nke Sussan Group (ARJ Holdings) nwere ma na-arụ ọrụ, bụ ndị nwekwara ma na-ahụ maka Sportsgirl na Suzanne Grae.
Ụlọ ahịa Sussan nke mbụ meghere na Little Collins Street, Melbourne na-ere uwe ime na 1939
Ka ọ na-erule njedebe nke 1951, e nwere ụlọ ahịa atọ na Little Collins Street, Collins Street na Swanston Street
Na 1953, ụlọ ahịa abụọ mbụ meghere na Adelaide sochiri ụlọ ahịa Perth na 1956
N'ime afọ 1960, oke Sussan toro karịa uwe akwa na uwe elu ọdịnala.
Ka ọ na-erule 1968, mgbasawanye ha gara n'ihu site n'ịzụta Chic Salon site na Woolworths, ụlọ ahịa akwa akwa 94 na-arụ ọrụ na Queensland na New South Wales
Nnweta a, yana ụlọ ahịa 60 dị na steeti ndịda na Western Australia, mere Sussan ọrụ mba.￼
N'afọ 1985, ụlọ ọrụ ahụ nwere ụlọ ahịa 200 na ngụkọta kwa afọ nke ihe dị ka $ 100 nde
Ọ bụ John Gandel na Marc Besen nwe ya, onye ọ bụla nwere òkè 50%
N'afọ ahụ, John Gandel rere òkè ya na ụlọ ọrụ ahụ nye Abraham Goldberg na Leon Lipkies, mgbe Gandel kpebiri ilekwasị anya na ọdịmma ụlọ ya
Goldberg na Lipkies nwere mmekọrịta azụmahịa dị na Besen site na "nchịkwa nke nnukwu ụlọ ọrụ akwa Australia" Entrad Corporation
Ngwakọta nke ụmụ nwoke atọ ahụ na Entrad ruru 76% nke ndị nwe ya.
N'afọ 2003, Naomi Milgrom, nwa nwa nke ndị guzobere Fay na Sam Gandel weghaara ikike nke otu ahụ mgbe ọ zụchara nne na nna ya na ụmụnne ya.
